title: REO Speedwagon - LIVE You Get What You Play For [320k MP3]
description:
Live: You Get What You Play For is a live album by rock band REO Speedwagon, which was released as a double-LP in 1977. It was recorded at Memorial Hall in Kansas City, Kansas, the Convention Center in Indianapolis, Indiana, Keil Auditorium in Saint Louis, Missouri, and the Electric Ballroom in Atlanta, Georgia.
